@node MAIN "Welcome"

@{b}Other programs @{ub}                                       @{"Deutsch" link /Andere.guide/Main}

   I have written some other little ARexx-programs for Wordworth. Some people will write these
   things for themselves, but maybe they are of help for some of you. I haven't translated all
   of them, sorry.

   @{"WW-Fontlist           " link Fontlist}  -  List of all fonts you have installed for Wordworth

   @{"WW-Print              " link Druck}  -  Print several documents one after another

   @{"WW-Farben             " link Farben}  -  Overview over the colours of WW

   @{"WW-Labels             " link Kaesten}  -  Print labels etc.

   @{"WW-Circles            " link Kreise}  -  conentric circles (if anybody needs that)

   @{"WW-FKeys              " link Fkeys}  -  Overview over F-Keys in WW (WW-Document)

   @{"Bibel                 " link Bibel}  -  Complex viewing program for bible texts. Should be possible to
                               use it for other long texts, too. Needs GoldEd and Muchmore.


   @{"Author                " link Autor}  -  Contact me!
@endnode
